summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1473, for the improvement of North and East Sixty-fifth Street, from East Green Lake Boulevard to Latona Avenue; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues therein named, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing the same, under Ordinance No. 15794 and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
